# Capacitor-generated native projects — initialize locally with:
#   npx cap add ios
#   npx cap add android
# (Uncomment the next two lines if you want to keep native projects out of git
#  entirely and re-add them on each fresh clone. Most teams commit them so the
#  iOS / Android side of the app — Info.plist, build settings, etc. — is
#  version-controlled.)
# ios/
# android/

